ªìn cung l·∫°i ch∆∞a ƒë·ªß. C&acirc;y yuzu th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c tr·ªìng ·ªü ƒê&ocirc;ng &Aacute; v&agrave; kh&oacute; canh t&aacute;c ·ªü nh·ªØng v&ugrave;ng ƒë·∫•t kh&aacute;c, c·∫ßn kh&aacute; nhi·ªÅu nƒÉm ƒë·ªÉ c&acirc;y ra qu·∫£. H∆°n n·ªØa n∆∞·ªõc trong yuzu kh&aacute; &iacute;t, ƒë·ªÉ kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m h∆∞ h·∫°i tr&aacute;i yuzu ng∆∞·ªùi ta ph·∫£i thu ho·∫°ch qu·∫£ b·∫±ng tay m&agrave; gi&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng kh&ocirc;ng h·ªÅ r·∫ª, do ƒë&oacute; gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh yuzu b·ªã ƒë·ªôi l&ecirc;n r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu. C&aacute;ch d·ªÖ t&igrave;m h∆°n l&agrave; b·∫°n c&oacute; th·ªÉ t&igrave;m mua n∆∞·ªõc c·ªët yuzu ƒë&oacute;ng chai, v&agrave; n·∫øu pha tr&agrave; l&agrave;m b&aacute;nh th&igrave; mua h≈© m·ª©t yuzu (yuzu honey) (ch·∫Øc ·ªü ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u ƒë&acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch duy nh·∫•t), d&ugrave; n&oacute; v·∫´n ƒë·∫Øt so v·ªõi c&aacute;c h≈© m·ª©t qu·∫£ kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&igrave; ƒë&acirc;y l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng th·ª©c ph&aacute;t sinh n&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ·∫£nh h∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m cho c&aacute;c b·∫°n, mong c&aacute;c b·∫°n th&ocirc;ng c·∫£m. C&aacute;ch l&agrave;m c≈©ng s·∫Ω t∆∞∆°ng t·ª± nh∆∞ cheesecake xo&agrave;i hay chanh leo th&ocirc;i nh&eacute; üòÄ</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2023/04/fresh-japanese-yuzu-1-1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2023/04/japanese-citrus-yuzu-4-1-1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Source ·∫£nh: White on rice couple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C&Ocirc;NG TH·ª®C:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; B&aacute;nh s·∫Ω g·ªìm c&oacute; 4 l·ªõp: l·ªõp b&aacute;nh quy l&agrave;m ƒë·∫ø, l·ªõp kem cheese, l·ªõp th·∫°ch yuzu nh&acirc;n gi·ªØa v&agrave; l·ªõp th·∫°ch chanh tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng th·ª©c n&agrave;y &aacute;p d·ª•ng cho khu&ocirc;n ring 15cm, c&ograve;n l·ªõp th·∫°ch nh&acirc;n gi·ªØa l&agrave; 12cm nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A.</strong>L·ªõp b&aac