\n\r\n<p>Hai trong nh·ªØng nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng n·ªïi ti·∫øng v&agrave; l&acirc;u ƒë·ªùi b&aacute;n v·ªãt quay ngon nh·∫•t ·ªü B·∫Øc Kinh l&agrave;&nbsp;<em><strong>Quanjude Beijing Duck Restaurant</strong></em>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<em><strong>Bianyifang ‰æøÂÆúÂùä</strong></em>. Quanjude ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·ªü l·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ti&ecirc;n v&agrave;o nƒÉm 1864 v&agrave; ph&aacute;t minh ra ph∆∞∆°ng ph&aacute;p quay v·ªãt ·ªü l&ograve; m·ªü ƒë∆∞·ª£c x&acirc;y t·ª´ g·∫°ch c&ograve;n Bianyifang ra ƒë&ograve;i s·ªõm h∆°n v&agrave; c&oacute; tu·ªïi ƒë·ªùi c·ª° 600 nƒÉm. ·ªû ƒë&acirc;y h·ªç c&oacute; cho th&ecirc;m h·∫°t sen, tr&agrave; ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát c&ugrave;ng t&aacute;o ƒë·ªè v&agrave;o b·ª•ng con v·ªãt tƒÉng th&ecirc;m h∆∞∆°ng v·ªã cho m&oacute;n ƒÉn, ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n c&oacute; v·ªãt quay nh·ªìi n∆∞·ªõc ninh rau c·ªß theo b&iacute; quy·∫øt ri&ecirc;ng n·ªØa. Do ch∆∞a ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª≠ v·ªãt quay chu·∫©n h&agrave;ng ·ªü nh·ªØng n∆°i n&agrave;y n&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh s·∫Ω kh&ocirc;ng ƒë∆∞a ra b·∫•t c·ª© b&igrave;nh lu·∫≠n l&agrave; b&ecirc;n n&agrave;o ngon h∆°n b&ecirc;n n&agrave;o, th·∫≠m ch&iacute; ƒë&aacute;nh gi&aacute; tr&ecirc;n m·∫°ng t·ª´ kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c≈©ng g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i v&igrave; m·ªói ng∆∞·ªùi m·ªôt kh·∫©u v·ªã ri&ecirc;ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh ƒë&atilde; l∆∞u l·∫°i t&ecirc;n 2 qu&aacute;n n&agrave;y ƒë·ªÉ sau c&oacute; d·ªãp sang b·ªÉn ph·∫£i ti·∫øt ki·ªám ti·ªÅn ƒÉn m·ªôt b·ªØa cho bi·∫øt üòÄ</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"20171215112549118\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2020/06/20171215112549118.jpg\" style=\"height:354px; width:640px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C·ª≠a l&ograve;. Ngu·ªìn: internet</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>S·ª± kh&aacute;c nhau gi·ªØa v·ªãt quay B·∫Øc Kinh v&agrave; v·ªãt quay Qu·∫£ng ƒê&ocirc;ng:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>ƒêi·ªÉm kh&aacute;c nhau l·ªõn ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; c&aacute;ch ch·∫ø bi·∫øn v·ªãt. ƒê·∫ßu ti&ecirc;n l&agrave; ph·∫ßn r·∫°ch tr&ecirc;n th&acirc;n con v·ªãt: v·ªãt B·∫Øc Kinh th&igrave; ƒë∆∞·ª£c r·∫°ch 1 l·ªó ngay