gi&ograve;n h∆°n n&ecirc;n th&iacute;ch h·ª£p l&agrave;m salad ho·∫∑c x&agrave;o. Ri&ecirc;ng lo·∫°i 7 l·ªó th&iacute;ch h·ª£p cho vi·ªác h·∫ßm ho·∫∑c n·∫•u canh v&igrave; ƒë·ªô gi&ograve;n k&eacute;m h∆°n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/mua-cu-sen-nen-chon-loai-7-hay-9-lo-moi-dai-bo-hinh-6.jpg?w=600\" style=\"height:450px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>·∫¢nh m·∫°ng: c·ªß sen 7 l·ªó (tr&aacute;i) v&agrave; 9 l·ªó (ph·∫£i)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M&oacute;n h&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh mu·ªën gi·ªõi thi·ªáu v·ªõi c&aacute;c b·∫°n ƒë&oacute; l&agrave; m&oacute;n c·ªß sen rim x&igrave; d·∫ßu ki·ªÉu H&agrave;n Yeon-geun-jorim Ïó∞Í∑ºÏ°∞Î¶º. M&oacute;n n&agrave;y v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng d·ªÖ n·∫•u, d·ªÖ ƒÉn v&agrave; nhanh g·ªçn, th&iacute;ch h·ª£p c·∫£ v·ªõi nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ƒÉn chay. Ng∆∞·ªùi H&agrave;n th∆∞·ªùng n·∫•u m&oacute;n c·ªß sen rim r·ªìi cho v&agrave;o c∆°m h·ªôp mang ƒëi, ho·∫∑c c&oacute; th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒÉn gi·ªëng nh∆∞ nh·ªØng m&oacute;n ƒÉn Banchan kh&aacute;c trong b·ªØa c∆°m c·ªßa ng∆∞·ªùi H&agrave;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N<strong>GUY&Ecirc;N LI·ªÜU:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>500gr c·ªß sen ƒë&atilde; l&agrave;m s·∫°ch (c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m s·∫°ch xem ·ªü ph·∫ßn c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m)</li>\r\n	<li>1,5 th&igrave;a ƒÉn d·∫ßu ƒÉn</li>\r\n	<li>60 ml x&igrave; d·∫ßu (d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mykitchies.com/2020/04/25/tu-bep-nha-minh-co-gi-cam-nang-gia-vi-p1/#xidau\" target=\"_blank\">h&atilde;ng Sempio ho·∫∑c Kikkoman</a>&nbsp;cho th∆°m b&ugrave;i, n·∫øu d&ugrave;ng Lee Kum Kee th&igrave; b·ªõt l·∫°i ƒë·ªÅ ph&ograve;ng b·ªã m·∫∑n) &ndash; kho·∫£ng 4 th&igrave;a ƒÉn</li>\r\n	<li>170ml sirup ng&ocirc; oligodang (Ïò¨Î¶¨Í≥†Îãπ) ho·∫∑c<a href=\"https://mykitchies.com/2020/05/17/tu-bep-minh-co-gi-cam-nang-gia-vi-p2/#sirogao\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;sirup g·∫°o (jocheong, Ï°∞Ï≤≠)&nbsp;</a>(kho·∫£ng 12 th&igrave;a ƒÉn)</li>\r\n	<li>1/2 th&igrave;a ƒÉn t·ªèi bƒÉm nhuy·ªÖn (kho·∫£ng 2 t&eacute;p t·ªèi) (t&ugrave;y ch·ªçn)</li>\r\n	<li>2 th&igrave;a cafe d·∫ßu m&egrave; (sesam oil)</li>\r\n	<li>1/2 &ndash; 1 th&igrave;a cafe m&egrave; rang</li>\r\n	<li>250ml n∆∞·ªõc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>L∆∞u &yacute;: th&agrave;nh ph·∫©m c·ªßa m&igrave;nh c&oacute; v·ªã ng·ªçt nh∆∞ng kh&ocirc;ng g·∫Øt v&igrave; m&igrave;nh d&ugrave;ng sirup g·∫°o c·ªßa H&agrave;n, n·∫øu c&aacute;c b·∫°n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng kho·∫£ng 8 th&igrave;a ƒÉn ƒë∆∞·ªùng n&acirc;u, ho·∫∑c gi·∫£m l∆∞·ª£ng ƒë∆∞·ªùng xu·ªëng c&ograve;n 1 n·ª≠a n·∫øu kh&ocirc;ng mu·ªën ƒÉn ng·ªçt. ƒê·ªÉ m&oacute;n ƒÉn chu·∫©n h∆°n ch&uacute;t th&igrave; m&igrave;nh khuy&ecirc;n n&ecirc;n mua sirup g·∫°o v&agrave; x&igrave; d·∫ßu c·ªßa H&agrave;n ƒë·ªÉ c&oacute; th·ªÉ d·∫≠y ƒë&uacute;ng m&ugrave;i th∆°m c·ªßa c&aacute;c lo·∫°i gia v·ªã.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/wp-1641732308366.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/wp-1641732308268.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C&Aacute;CH L&Agrave;M:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/wp-1641732308314.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/wp-1641732308215.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/wp-1641732308148.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>N·∫øu d&ugrave;ng c·ªß sen t∆∞∆°i, c&aacute;c b·∫°n c·∫Øt b·ªè 2 ƒë·∫ßu r·ªìi d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;i b&agrave;o v·ªè c&agrave; r·ªët b&agrave;o v·ªè c·ªß sen, sau ƒë&oacute; c·∫Øt th&agrave;nh t·ª´ng l&aacute;t kho·∫£ng 6-7mm. Ti·∫øp ƒë&oacute; ng&acirc;m c·ªß sen v&agrave;o n∆∞·ªõc l·∫°nh kho·∫£ng 30 ph&uacute;t r·ªìi ƒëem ƒëi lu·ªôc c&ugrave;ng 1 th&igrave;a ƒÉn gi·∫•m trong 5 ph&uacute;t, kh&ocirc;ng ƒë·∫≠y vung nh&eacute;. Lu·ªôc xong ƒëem ƒëi r·ª≠a l·∫°i v·ªõi n∆∞·ªõc.</li>\r\n	<li>D&ugrave;ng m·ªôt c&aacute;i ch·∫£o r·ªìi ƒëun n&oacute;ng d·∫ßu, cho c·ªß sen v&agrave;o x&agrave;o s∆° kho·∫£ng 3-5 ph&uacute;t. Cho 250ml n∆∞·ªõc c&ugrave;ng x&igrave; d·∫ßu, t·ªèi bƒÉm v&agrave;o, ƒëun s&ocirc;i r·ªìi h·∫° l·ª≠a nh·ªè v·ª´a, ƒë·∫≠y vung v&agrave; rim trong kho·∫£ng 35-40 ph&uacute;t, l&acirc;u l&acirc;u ƒë·∫£o qua cho ƒë·ªÅu. N·∫øu nhanh c·∫°n n∆∞·ªõc th&igrave; c&aacute;c b·∫°n h·∫° l·ª≠a nh·ªè h∆°n v&agrave; ch&acirc;m x&iacute;u n∆∞·ªõc v&agrave;o n·∫øu c·∫ßn.</li>\r\n	<li>Sau ƒë&oacute; cho sirup g·∫°o, ƒë·∫£o ƒë·ªÅu r·ªìi ƒë·∫≠y vung rim ti·∫øp t·∫ßm 15-20 ph&uacute;t. Sau ƒë&oacute; m·ªü vung v&agrave; ƒë·ªÉ l·ª≠a to v·ª´a, nh·ªõ ƒë·∫£o ƒë·ªÅu cho t·ªõi khi c·ªß sen b&aacute;m s·ªët v&agrave; tr&ocirc;ng b&oacute;ng h∆°n, s·ªët c≈©ng c·∫°n. L&uacute;c ƒë&oacute; th&igrave; t·∫Øt b·∫øp, cho d·∫ßu m&egrave; v&agrave; m&egrave; rang v&agrave;o.</li>\r\n	<li>Th&agrave;nh ph·∫©m ƒÉn c&ugrave;ng c∆°m, c&oacute; th·ªÉ b·∫£o qu·∫£n trong ngƒÉn m&aacute;t t·ªß l·∫°nh kho·∫£ng 10-12 ng&agrave;y trong h·ªôp k&iacute;n.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mykitchies.files.wordpress.com/2022/01/3.jpg?w=768\" style=\"height:1080px; width:810px\" /></p>\r\n', '1731858192_2-768x1152.jpg', '2024-11-17', 1);

